Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三次…世界大战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争的结果是 到2036年时全世界已经有57亿人丧生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而战争的契机就是…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？这是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.35,0:00:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是机器人吧？会变形什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是时间机器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是叔叔 果然认识啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就好说了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.79,0:00:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从α世界线来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这三周之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无数次 无数次的改变世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:52.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至不惜牺牲了红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才到达了这个β世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让这一切成为徒劳…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.03,0:01:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.74,0:01:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像之前在广播馆被刺杀的科学家就叫这个名字哎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈部伦太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.59,0:01:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我说为了回避世界大战所需要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.49,0:01:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是拯救在2010年7月28日死去的牧瀬红莉栖呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细情况我也不了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我接到的任务只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是拯救牧瀬红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:42.45,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(572,660)}Attractor Field
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且到达不受世界线收束范围影响的唯一的世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:45.18,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(685,660)}Steins gate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.25,0:01:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往命运石之门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.81,0:03:20.86,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(690,660)}境界面上的命运石之门
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.31,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(620,660)}Steins gate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.39,0:03:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运石之门？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,设立这个计划的 是未来的叔叔和父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现阶段一切都只是推测
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你们两个的理论是错的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:40.63,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(665,660)}Steins gate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.53,0:03:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不存在命运石之门这条世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过即使如此我也还是要去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上会有一个美好未来在等待的这个未知可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果叔叔愿意和我一起去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.82,0:03:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就握住这只手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…真由喜虽然对刚才这番话一头雾水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.31,0:04:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个叫做红莉栖小姐的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果对冈伦来说是很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那冈伦不是该努力一下才对吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.10,0:04:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得第三次世界大战之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和冈伦的妄想太接近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.06,0:04:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以根本就没别的人能依靠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对未来的57亿人的性命没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.79,0:04:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快搭乘上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.99,0:04:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能坐两个人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 这可是出自我父亲之手的最高杰作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把手机留下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:05:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为可能会跟那边叔叔带的手机产生混淆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是时间机器？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 虽然我已经搭乘它去过1975年以及2000年了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过运行状态良好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.07,0:05:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 燃料要吃紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 它也能从过去跳向未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了 因为是时间机器啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.18,0:05:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为和那时的世界线不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去的是7月28日12点前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为到达的地点是无法更改的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要是去的太早
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会在广播馆引起骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会改变牧瀬红莉栖的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次坐的话 估计会有很严重的重力反应
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以做好心理准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.93,0:06:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.06,0:06:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然会出现的东西 就像是时光碎片一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我胃液倒流了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不像话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免与这个时间点上的自己接触
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:37.53,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(859,660)}time paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.15,0:06:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那样会引起严重的时间悖论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离她被刺还有多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该还有大约20分钟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去设置时间机器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔去保护她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我叔叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.05,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月28日 我看到红莉栖倒在血泊中的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:07:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和真由理一起参加了中钵博士的见面会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后听到了楼顶上发出的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说起来 真由理等一下会去7楼乌帕的扭蛋机那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是为了这个才叫我过来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个系列已经没剩多少了 但真由喜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:30.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百元硬币用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法 从里面的楼梯回到8楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金属的啊 金属乌帕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.09,0:07:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很稀有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 超级稀有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来到这里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:45.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖还…活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在哪里见过面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.19,0:07:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:07:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在听我说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.20,0:08:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:05.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回答我的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.15,0:08:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.72,0:08:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…把你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:19.95,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 位于8楼大厅的中钵博士见面会即将召开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.39,0:08:25.67,Default_tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 位于8楼大厅的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:32.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间机器的基本构造如你们所见已经印在了发给大家的资料上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此我就只说明一下基础理论
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今为止…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就计划书上来说 叔叔你应该要一直尾随牧瀬红莉栖才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.65,0:08:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 把她带去外面也很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能确认杀死她的凶手跟原因的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到头来很有可能还是一样走向死亡的收束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟真由理那时一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.11,0:08:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博～士！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了啊？这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的时间机器理论是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克尔黑洞 世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.59,0:09:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是约翰·提托…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久 红莉栖就将在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.18,0:09:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是在别的地方被刺了 然后再被搬到这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 这个可能性也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.52,0:09:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然接下来会在这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在看的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间机器？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以红莉栖在每次世界线改变后都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 混账小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…希望您能看看这个 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是中钵博士？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.56,0:10:04.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸时隔七年联系了我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了让我来见面会对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:08.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事就成为了契机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.93,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到 红莉栖的父亲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我整理了脑海中浮现的理论 觉得没准真的能制造出时间机器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听听爸爸的意见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这篇论文能被承认的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.63,0:10:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被逐出学会的爸爸也能卷土重来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是被逐出去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我看不惯他们 然后主动离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.59,0:10:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 只要爸爸你不介意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为可以跟爸爸共同署名发表这篇论文
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.03,0:10:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为契机是爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么傻话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.67,0:10:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这篇论文会署上我一个人的名字然后发表
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道爸爸你打算盗用我的论文吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.01,0:10:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为只有这种事您是绝对不会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:10:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.47,0:11:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然敢说我盗用？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么就这么优秀啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没道理孩子比父母还要优秀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.22,0:11:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是没有你 我就能一直保持优秀了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没有你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们事先商量好了 想要搞砸我的见面会对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.62,0:11:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…保护红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别把我当笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧 爸爸 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别对我指手画脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:12.78,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.20,0:12:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又明白些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感受 我的这份屈辱 我身处的地狱…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.06,0:12:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要没有你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.53,0:12:37.49,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红…红莉栖？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:13:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个笨蛋 真是和你们无比相衬的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 把你也牵扯进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是我父亲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想得到爸爸的认同 仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.29,0:13:16.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…还不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想…死…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.62,0:13:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:08.45,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了 杀了 杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦 你那满身的血是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 这不是叔叔的血
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.75,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我杀了…是我杀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.63,0:14:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…杀了红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我杀了红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我杀了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔我知道你很痛苦 但还不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.74,0:14:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间机器还留有再一次回到过去的燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了 就算再回去也一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:38.37,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(499,660)}Attractor Field
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.82,0:14:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正因为世界线收束范围的收束 红莉栖总会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 冈伦的手机…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮件？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.11,0:14:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 打开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs54\be2\fr-12\an1\move(204,578,191,545,600,1900)\t(600,1900,1,\fs70)}看电视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看电视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中钵博士搭乘的飞机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.72,0:15:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs45\fr27\pos(653,581)\c&HB5B4B1&}中钵博士 逃亡俄罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然货物舱起火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但好像仍然勉强在逃亡目的地的俄罗斯着陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过话说回来 真是得救了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠这个东西被金属探测器发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以论文没有被大火烧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.32,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.57,0:15:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是真由喜的金属乌帕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.64,0:15:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里还写着真由喜的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哎 但是为什么在俄罗斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那篇论文就是一切的起因
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.07,0:15:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此为契机 大国之间展开了激烈的时间机器开发竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只要能统帅时间 就等于统帅了全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 最终发展成为了世界大战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事关57亿人的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.41,0:15:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救红莉栖 然后改变世界线吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.87,0:15:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟真由理那时是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论我怎么挣扎 结果都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红莉栖还是会死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.10,0:16:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就是一次失败…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说傻话了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我已经失败过几次…几十次了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.63,0:16:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时间之环究竟有多么不讲情理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.89,0:16:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有究竟会准备好多么残酷的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我其实早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:30.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.71,0:16:35.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦不是那种会半途而废的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由喜是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦绝对不是那种轻言放弃的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连真由喜无法跟奶奶说再见的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.21,0:16:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦也从未放弃 每天都会跟去墓地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.07,0:17:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真由喜才跟奶奶告别了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以真由喜才变得这么有精神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.03,0:17:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…不能放弃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月28日那天 应该有收到一封影音邮件才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.61,0:17:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7月28日…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.48,0:17:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的话应该可以看了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是「拯救牧瀬红莉栖已经失败过一次」的现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 瞒着没告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.48,0:17:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要经历过一次失败其实也在计划之内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了让叔叔看到这段影像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.48,0:17:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是初次见面吧 15年前的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是冈伦啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.74,0:17:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你既然已经打开了这封邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就意味着你在拯救红莉栖这事上已经失败过一次了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过正是这份痛苦 给予了我执念
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能把它当做是「未曾发生过的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换句话说 这是相当于「事前准备」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来终于可以进入计划的正题了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:22.91,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(824,660)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.17,0:18:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救牧瀬红莉栖 并且进入命运石之门的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条件有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个是把中钵博士带到俄罗斯的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于时间机器的论文
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从这个世界上抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.15,0:18:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一个 就是拯救牧瀬红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是真能做到这件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 想要回避牧瀬红莉栖的死亡并且改变过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.93,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(461,660)}Attractor Field
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点由于世界线收束范围的收束而成为了不可能的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就明说了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救红莉栖是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是方法有误而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.14,0:18:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我仔细听好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.06,0:19:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能改变既定的过去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.84,0:19:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让一开始你自己见到的事情变成「未曾发生过的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是变成「未曾发生过」的话 就会造成过去改变
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.75,0:19:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让一切都付诸东流
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回想起你在α世界线所经历的一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只有短短三个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你应该还记得跟红莉栖一同度过的时间才对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟红莉栖一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.82,0:19:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了拯救真由理而牺牲了许多回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断挣扎的这份经历 应该还存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.86,0:19:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能让你那三个星期的世界线漂流白费
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也绝对不能把它当做「未曾发生过的事」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为你到达过无数条世界线
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以渴望拯救红莉栖的你才存在于那里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把一切都奉献给时间机器开发的我才存在于这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在所身处的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.00,0:19:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为我们都渴望着拯救红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能到达的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 去欺骗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不改变「红莉栖已死」这个过去的情况下救活她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让过去的自己将还活着的红莉栖「观测」为已死的红莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做的话 就不会引发过去改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.54,0:20:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.05,0:20:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦你明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话应该能明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.57,0:20:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺带一提 时间机器的型号是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C204型
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.36,0:20:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首字母到底意味着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.61,0:20:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不着我说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯蒂娜（Cristina）…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:41.03,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(839,660)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外将目的地的世界线命名为命运石之门的也是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是这个名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的话应该也能明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.91,0:20:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「并没有什么意义」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:58.46,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(625,660}Operation Skuld
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 对最终任务『掌管未来的女神』作战的概要进行说明
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.80,0:21:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不改变既定过去的情况下改变结果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「浑身是血倒在地上的牧濑红莉栖」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.85,0:21:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及「目睹了这一切的冈部伦太郎」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不改变这些既定过去的条件下改变结果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.92,0:21:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗最初的你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.47,0:21:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗世界！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:21.78,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(708,660)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是到达命运石之门的条件
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,El Psy Congroo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.63,0:21:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚那个是15年后的冈伦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音好低沉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:48.90,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(675,660}Operation Skuld
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说『掌管未来的女神』？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然说El Psy Congroo？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都33岁了我还在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:21:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就是中二病全开嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.31,0:22:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冈伦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.02,0:22:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就做到这一切给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:08.56,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(708,660)}Steins Gate
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果说这就是命运石之门的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.88,0:22:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是狂气的科学狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.29,0:22:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤凰院凶真！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺骗世界这种小事 不值一提！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.52,0:22:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦 变回平时的那个冈伦了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.81,0:22:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是呢 真由喜还是更喜欢这样的冈伦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.03,0:22:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我再说一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.68,0:22:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是狂气的科学狂人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凤凰院凶真！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.46,0:22:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界 是我的掌中之物！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:10.38,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去は離れて行き 未来は近づくの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:15.85,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,観測者はいつか 矛盾に気付く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:26.78,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神の創り出した世界は 完全なるもので 絶対の均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:33.66,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは折り重なる偶然 宇宙規模の奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:39.57,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守られてきた ゲート「規制」は終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:40.85,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open The Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:46.45,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「0」が過去で 「1」が未来 「今」は何処にもない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:51.40,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背く事の出来ぬロジック
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.29,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open The Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:58.00,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並行する無数の線 選択は冒涜へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:03.34,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らの「存在」さえ疑う
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:09.79,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その目に映る景色は「収束」をする
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:30.76,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二つの針が指す 時間の概念も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:36.31,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,観測者しだいで 歪みを見せる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:47.31,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神に与えられた英知は 必ず「果て」がある 絶対の領域
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:54.22,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは愚かな故の偶然 招かれざる奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:23:00.15,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉ざされてきたゲート「規制」は終わった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:01.25,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open The Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:06.94,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光速へと手を伸ばした 想い出のパルスが
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.12,0:23:11.97,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛び込む不可思議なロジック
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:12.83,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Open The Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.01,0:23:18.46,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙がまだ隠し持った 秩序のない理論
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:23.61,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限と呼ばれた点と点が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.51,0:23:30.54,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正な力を借りて「再生」をする
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:10.38,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去在在远离 未来正在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.96,0:21:15.85,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测者总有一天会发现矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.01,0:21:26.78,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神所创造出来的世界 是完美之物 拥有绝对的均衡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:33.66,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是重叠在一起的偶然 引发出宇宙规模的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:39.57,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被守护着的 Gate 终于结束「限制」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:40.85,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:46.45,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「0」是过去 「1」是未来 「现在」则不曾存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:51.40,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法违背的逻辑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.29,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.46,0:21:58.00,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并行排列的无数条线 选择终将变为冒渎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:22:03.34,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连我们的「存在」都会被质疑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:09.79,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼中映出的景色也终会「收束」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.57,0:22:30.76,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连两枚指针所指出的时间概念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:36.31,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会向观测者展现它的扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:47.31,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由神所赋予的睿智 也终究会有「极限」 这是绝对的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.94,0:22:54.22,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是由于愚蠢的偶然 所招致而来的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.38,0:23:00.15,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被紧闭的Gate 终于结束「限制」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:01.25,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.43,0:23:06.94,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着光速伸出双手 回忆的脉冲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.12,0:23:11.97,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞入不可思议的逻辑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.14,0:23:12.83,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.01,0:23:18.46,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙还未显露出的 毫无秩序的理论
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:23.61,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称作无限的点与点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.51,0:23:30.54,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借助不正当的力量进行「回放」
